digiKam 9.1.0 - Release date: 2026-xx-xx

*****************************************************************************************************
NEW FEATURES:

Bundles component versions:

(*): Updated compared to previous digiKam release.

| Bundles       | Qt version | KDE version | OpenCV version | FFmpeg version | Heif version | ExifTool version | Exiv2 version | Build Environment   |
|---------------|------------|-------------|----------------|----------------|--------------|------------------|---------------|---------------------|
| Windows Qt5   | 5.15.17    | 5.116       | 4.11           | 7.1.1          | 1.20.2       | 13.52            | 0.28.5        | Windows 10 + VCPKG  |
| Windows Qt6   | 6.10.1 (*) | 6.23.0 (*)  | 4.12 (*)       | 8.0.1 (*)      | 1.21.2 (*)   | 13.52            | 0.28.8 (*)    | Windows 11 + VCPKG  |
| AppImage Qt5  | 5.15.18    | 5.116       | 4.13 (*)       | 8.0.1 (*)      | 1.21.2 (*)   | 13.52            | 0.28.8 (*)    | XUbuntu 20.06       |
| AppImage Qt6  | 6.10.2 (*) | 6.24.0 (*)  | 4.13 (*)       | 8.0.1 (*)      | 1.21.2 (*)   | 13.52            | 0.28.8 (*)    | XUbuntu 22.04       |
| macOS Qt5     | 5.15.18    | 5.116       | 4.12           | 7.1.2          | 1.20.2       | 13.52            | 0.28.7        | Monterey + Macports |
| macOS Qt6     | 6.10.0     | 6.20.0      | 4.12           | 7.1.2          | 1.20.2       | 13.52            | 0.28.7        | Sequoia + Macports  |

Raw Engine      : Internal Libraw has been updated to the latest upstream 20260310 which brings with
                  it a variety of bug fixes and performance improvements.
Import          : USB Mass Storage driver now support video thumbnails.

*****************************************************************************************************
BUGFIXES:

001 --> 517251 - MariaSQL Migration.
002 --> 517308 - In the new "Survey" tool, the left and right overlay navigation arrows are not working.
003 --> 517303 - Modification date is not being edited.
004 --> 517328 - Error when starting digiKam 9.0.0 - lensfun.dll.
005 --> 517393 - Faces menu when viewing an image preview is showing image_recognize_faces instead of the label.
006 --> 517420 - Changing rating filter does not result in immediate view update.
007 --> 517449 - Unable to create a face region.
008 --> 517441 - Grouping by Filename is behaving differently on MacOS than on Linux Mint.
009 --> 517484 - Network error message while using reverse geocoding with OpenStreetMap.
010 --> 517538 - Shortcuts not working in Survey module.
011 --> 517354 - Images seem to be gone when upgrading from 8.8.0 with mariadb on NAS (but are still in DB).
012 --> 517560 - Short key for flags do not work in new survey screen.
013 --> 516875 - OpenCL not detected on AMD RADEON RX 470 card.
014 --> 517588 - Cut and paste crash, jas_init_library: Assertion `!jas_global.initialized' failed.
015 --> 517585 - Import from SD-card without being asked for an album.
016 --> 517558 - Finalizing Tags removes EXIF Copyright and Artist entries.
017 --> 511588 - Portable archive for 8.8.0 (digiKam-8.8.0-Qt6-Win64.tar.xz) is missing as a download option.
018 --> 517624 - Filtering on rating (stars 0-5) not working correct.
019 --> 517671 - Rating filter do not work.
020 --> 517668 - Show placeholders for other files in the album.
021 --> 517772 - Bug after update libexiv2-27.
022 --> 517766 - Crash on App startup.
023 --> 517299 - Opening Geolocation Editor crashes digiKam.
024 --> 517757 - Clicking on a "Help" button in a dialog causes digiKam to silently disappear.
